BILL.EXE - FOR EGA OR BETTER                              12/29/91
  This is my first attempt at programming in assembler and I wrote all the
graphics routines and stuff without really knowing what I'm doing. It is
entirely possibly that this program won't run on your system or worse.
If it works, however, you will be dazzled by 120 images of the immortal
BILL THE CAT, which will randomly wink at you and eventually burn into
your monitor if you leave it running long enough (which I highly recommend.)
